        {
            "+content": "Pythagoras Production produces its new idol unit, \"Marginal #4.\" Its members, Atom Kirihara, Rui Aiba, L Nomura, and R Nomura, are the idols who will deliver their kiss to the ends of the galaxy. Outside the stage they are just normal high schoolers with their own problems. In Pythagoras Production they continue to mature as idols along with the help of the already famous senior unit, Lagrange Point, and the younger unit who expect to make their debut, Unicorn Jr. This is the tale of Margninal #4, a school slice-of-life about idols that shine brighter than the stars. Produced by J.C.Staff, based on the CD Drama and Visual Novel.",
